4. `Load` (real) — reads the file
5. `Stamp`, `Save`, `Rename` — moves the file
6. `fl.Release`

The reject's rename happens AFTER the reject takes the lock, which is at T=150ms. So at T=1ms, the file should still be in inProgressDir.

